cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with pre-training and learning from existing data in Reinforcement Learning. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it proposes a new method for learning from observational data. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) as it deals with control tasks in RL. Finally, it could also be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as RL is often used in computer vision tasks.
